\begin_layout Standard
One possibility for this behavior could be because laboratory reared flies
 (Canton S flies were used in this assay) tend to fly much closer to their
 maximum WBF at rest 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "Bhandawat:2010eu"

\end_inset

